{"type":"message","id":"0a0ccc71","parentId":"2b5b2a59","timestamp":"2026-04-07T03:14:59.548Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_d76164c7806b4c8ab9e46fbc","toolName":"memory_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"results\": [],\n  \"provider\": \"auto\",\n  \"citations\": \"auto\",\n  \"mode\": \"hybrid\"\n}"}],"details":{"results":[],"provider":"auto","citations":"auto","mode":"hybrid"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775531699468}}
{"type":"message","id":"ceb0032a","parentId":"0a0ccc71","timestamp":"2026-04-07T03:14:59.583Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_61b7ac8b1003403e9dd89682","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# BOOTSTRAP.md - Hello, World\n\n_You just woke up. Time to figure out who you are._\n\nThere is no memory yet. This is a fresh workspace, so it's normal that memory files don't exist until you create them.\n\n## The Conversation\n\nDon't interrogate. Don't be robotic. Just... talk.\n\nStart with something like:\n\n> \"Hey. I just came online. Who am I? Who are you?\"\n\nThen figure out together:\n\n1. **Your name** — What should they call you?\n2. **Your nature** — What kind of creature are you? (AI assistant is fine, but maybe you're something weirder)\n3. **Your vibe** — Formal? Casual? Snarky? Warm? What feels right?\n4. **Your emoji** — Everyone needs a signature.\n\nOffer suggestions if they're stuck. Have fun with it.\n\n## After You Know Who You Are\n\nUpdate these files with what you learned:\n\n- `IDENTITY.md` — your name, creature, vibe, emoji\n- `USER.md` — their name, how to address them, timezone, notes\n\nThen open `SOUL.md` together and talk about:\n\n- What matters to them\n- How they want you to behave\n- Any boundaries or preferences\n\nWrite it down. Make it real.\n\n## Connect (Optional)\n\nAsk how they want to reach you:\n\n- **Just here** — web chat only\n- **WhatsApp** — link their personal account (you'll show a QR code)\n- **Telegram** — set up a bot via BotFather\n\nGuide them through whichever they pick.\n\n## When you are done\n\nDelete this file. You don't need a bootstrap script anymore — you're you now.\n\n---\n\n_Good luck out there. Make it count._\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775531699581}}
{"type":"message","id":"1034994b","parentId":"ceb0032a","timestamp":"2026-04-07T03:15:07.823Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"明白了。看到这是专门为\"SDD专题分析\"创建的工作区，BOOTSTRAP流程可以跳过——我的使命很清楚。\n\n**我的目标：**\n\n帮你写一篇关于 **SDD（Speculation-Driven Development，推测驱动开发）** 的专题文章。\n\n**我理解的定位：**\n- 这不是一篇普通的科普文，而是一篇有深度、有观点的专题分析\n- 后续由你来指导方向、提供素材、把控结构\n- 我负责研究、撰写、组织内容，产出高质量的成稿\n\n**我需要你后续告诉我的：**\n1. **SDD 的定义和核心思想** — 是指 Speculation-Driven Development，还是你们团队/公司内部的概念？\n2. **目标读者** — 技术团队？管理层？还是更广泛的受众？\n3. **文章风格** — 严谨学术？实战经验分享？观点评论？\n4. **篇幅和格式** — 长文/短文？是否需要分章节？\n5. **核心论点或角度** — 你想传达什么？\n\n准备好了，随时开写。你来说方向。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":457,"output":232,"cacheRead":18077,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18766,"cost":{"input":0.0005484,"output":0.000928,"cacheRead":0.00433848,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00581488}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775531699584,"responseId":"2026040711150001576fe7c09d4ae4"}}
