{"type":"message","id":"e9d4b293","parentId":"d2a1c3e2","timestamp":"2026-04-07T06:41:36.360Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"资料整理完毕，先汇报关键补充内容，再问你几个问题。\n\n---\n\n## 方法论补充汇总\n\n在你之前列出的基础上，我补全了 **5 大类、20+ 种方法论/实践**：\n\n### 你提到的\n- **Spec Kit** — 规格测试框架（你实践过）\n- **Superpowers** — 需要你确认具体是什么\n- **Kiro** — AWS 的 AI 编码工具，主打 **Executable Specs**，核心理念是\"Go from vibe coding to viable code\"\n- **OpenSpec** — 你看过但没深入，我需要更多信息\n\n### 补充收集的\n\n**经典流派：** 形式化方法(Z/VDM/TLA+)、Design by Contract、TDD、BDD、Specification by Example、Model-Based Testing\n\n**API/契约驱动：** API-First(Stripe是标杆)、Consumer-Driven Contract Testing(Pact)、IDL(Protobuf/Thrift)\n\n**属性/类型驱动：** Property-Based Testing(QuickCheck/Hypothesis)、Type-Driven Development、Algebraic Design\n\n**AI 新范式：** Spec-Driven AI Development(Kiro)、Prompt as Specification、AI-Native Contract Testing、Spec-to-Code Generation\n\n### 大厂实践案例\n已覆盖 Amazon(TLA+)、Google(TDD+Protobuf)、Stripe(API-First)、Netflix(Contract Testing)、Meta(PBT)、Tesla(MBD)、WhatsApp(PropEr) 等 10 家。\n\n---\n\n## 需要你补充的问题\n\n1. **Spec Kit** — 你能简单说说它的核心理念和你的使用感受吗？\n2. **Superpowers** — 具体指什么产品/框架？\n3. **OpenSpec** — 哪个组织的？你了解多少？\n4. 还有其他你想关注的 SDD 工具/方法论吗？\n5. 大厂案例里有没有你想重点深入或补充的？\n6. **文章结构草案** 我初步拟了一个五章结构（发展脉络→方法论图谱→本质→问题→AI时代），你看看方向对不对？\n\n等你回复后我就开始正式写作。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":2729,"output":442,"cacheRead":26228,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29399,"cost":{"input":0.0032748,"output":0.0017679999999999998,"cacheRead":0.006294719999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01133752}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775544073125,"responseId":"20260407144113c9182d275ecd465d"}}
{"type":"message","id":"a2db8cbe","parentId":"e9d4b293","timestamp":"2026-04-07T07:31:38.637Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-04-07 15:31 GMT+8] Spec Kit — 你能简单说说它的核心理念和你的使用感受吗？\n你应该通过自己收集的资料判断，我的感受暂时不告诉你，避免误导你\n\nSuperpowers — 具体指什么产品/框架？\n你自己收集不到相关资料？还是不确定？\n\nOpenSpec — 哪个组织的？你了解多少？\n你自己收集不到相关资料？还是不确定？\n\n还有其他你想关注的 SDD 工具/方法论吗？\n要看你收集到的资料，我之前看过和实践过的SDD都和你说了。\n\n大厂案例里有没有你想重点深入或补充的？\n没有什么，我看到案例基本都是某个SDD的具体实践\n\n文章结构草案 我初步拟了一个五章结构（发展脉络→方法论图谱→本质→问题→AI时代），你看看方向对不对？\n问题不大，后续再调整\n\n另外对于AI Coding这个事的思考，当AI代码贡献率无限接见100%的时候，如何保障代码质量，SDD是一种好的选择吗？\n规格文档也是AI生成，如何保障质量呢？人工去check是否吞噬AI带来的效率优势？\n还有其他问题吗？"}],"timestamp":1775547098634}}
{"type":"message","id":"ef9a9483","parentId":"a2db8cbe","timestamp":"2026-04-07T07:31:55.893Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好问题。让我先集中精力收集 Spec Kit、Superpowers、OpenSpec 的资料，同时深入思考你提出的 AI 编码质量保障问题。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8d73ce3064834195b7d598f7","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -L --max-time 15 \"https://duckduckgo.com/html/?q=Spec+Kit+specification+testing+framework+software+development\" 2>&1 | grep -iE '(spec.kit|spec-kit|spec kit)' | head -20","timeout":20}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3ae59473d8f24e38bd29b0cf","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -L --max-time 15 \"https://duckduckgo.com/html/?q=Superpowers+specification+driven+development+AI+coding\" 2>&1 | grep -iE '(superpowers)' | head -20","timeout":20}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_19abf91d97d94c9b885c6f62","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -L --max-time 15 \"https://duckduckgo.com/html/?q=OpenSpec+specification+driven+development+AI+coding+tool\" 2>&1 | grep -iE '(openspec)' | head -20","timeout":20}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":28187,"output":242,"cacheRead":1491,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29920,"cost":{"input":0.0338244,"output":0.000968,"cacheRead":0.00035783999999999995,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.03515023999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775547098636,"responseId":"20260407153142214e030effa84b81"}}
