e":"www.53ai.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"4fe46fc9d582e199\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\n多 Ai 协同 + Sdd 编程实践：一个 Ai 全流程交付实录 - 今日头条\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"4fe46fc9d582e199\">>>","url":"https://www.toutiao.com/article/7601028280992514560/","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"5665f0378fc4c1bd\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\n本文基于 SDD 范式，构建了一套由 Claude Code、CodeX 与 Gemini 协同驱动的 AI Coding工作流，并成功从零交付一个跨境保险产品。\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"5665f0378fc4c1bd\">>>","siteName":"www.toutiao.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"8c24acf31c855564\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nOpenSpec — AI 原生规范驱动开发系统\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"8c24acf31c855564\">>>","url":"https://radebit.github.io/OpenSpec-Docs-zh/","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"90061b636793c8a5\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\n让 AI 编码助手 真正理解你的意图 OpenSpec 是 AI -Native 的规范驱动开发系统，为 AI 编码助手提供轻量级规范层。 在第一行代码编写之前，先与 AI 对齐需求，让开发过程更可预测、更高效。\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"90061b636793c8a5\">>>","siteName":"radebit.github.io"}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775552702926}}
{"type":"message","id":"27d9fe30","parentId":"feca6871","timestamp":"2026-04-07T09:05:03.033Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_f82667d2639147c5b232dae4","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"specification driven development SDD AI coding enterprise practice 2025 2026 comparison\",\n  \"provider\": \"duckduckgo\",\n  \"count\": 10,\n  \"tookMs\": 2991,\n  \"externalContent\": {\n    \"untrusted\": true,\n    \"source\": \"web_search\",\n    \"provider\": \"duckduckgo\",\n    \"wrapped\": true\n  },\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"d458f20c93eb620d\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nSpec-Driven Development: From Code to Contract in the Age of AI Coding ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"d458f20c93eb620d\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://arxiv.org/html/2602.00180v1\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"f2ae7fd82c407eae\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nSpec- driven development ( SDD ) [2, 4] offers an alternative: make the specification the source of truth, and let code derive from it. Instead of coding first and documenting later (or never), teams write clear specifications of intended behavior, then generate, implement, or verify code against those specifications .\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"f2ae7fd82c407eae\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"arxiv.org\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"3a7194bcb3ad22a8\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAgentic Coding: GSD vs Spec Kit vs OpenSpec vs Taskmaster AI: Where SDD ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"3a7194bcb3ad22a8\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://pub.spillwave.com/agentic-coding-gsd-vs-spec-kit-vs-openspec-vs-taskmaster-ai-where-sdd-tools-diverge-0414dcb97e46\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"883b0c153fd10dd3\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nSpec- driven development has gone mainstream. The premise is straightforward: define what you want before writing code, then let AI agents generate the implementation from structured specifications . In early 2025 , this was a niche workflow. By early 2026 , four spec- driven development tools with a combined 137,000+ GitHub stars have turned it into a movement.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"883b0c153fd10dd3\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"pub.spillwave.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"a237ff4b76fc3649\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nSpec-Driven Development (SDD): A Technical Deep Dive into the ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"a237ff4b76fc3649\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.rushis.com/spec-driven-development-sdd-a-technical-deep-dive-into-the-methodologies-reshaping-ai-assisted-engineering/\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"e199d166f8cc9a92\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nVibe coding broke as fast as it shipped. Spec- Driven Development is the industry's course correction — putting structured specs, not chat prompts, at the center of AI -assisted engineering. This post compares the leading SDD frameworks, their trade-offs, and when (or whether) to adopt one.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"e199d166f8cc9a92\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.rushis.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"92fbdaf374eef6f0\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nSpec-driven development: Unpacking one of 2025's key new AI-assisted ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"92fbdaf374eef6f0\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.thoughtworks.com/en-us/insights/blog/agile-engineering-practices/spec-driven-development-unpacking-2025-new-engineering-practices\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"720b772c871efe3a\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nDefining spec- driven development and competing interpretations of it My understanding of spec- driven development ( SDD ) is that it's a development paradigm that uses well-crafted software requirement specifications as prompts, aided by AI coding agents, to generate executable code.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"720b772c871efe3a\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.thoughtworks.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"47452defc128ade8\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nComplete Guide to Spec Coding (SDD): The Path to AI Engineering at ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"47452defc128ade8\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://qubittool.com/blog/spec-coding-complete-guide\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"b0d9fbbb021f48ca\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nTL;DR: If Vibe Coding lets you \\\"run fast,\\\" Spec Coding (Spec- Driven Development , SDD ) ensures you \\\"run far.\\\" In 2026 , the engineering consensus is clear: in the AI era, code is no longer the asset— the specification is the asset. And OpenSpec is the most widely adopted open-source framework for putting this into practice . This article deconstructs this structured paradigm and teaches you how ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"b0d9fbbb021f48ca\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"qubittool.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"f380cab5dd613857\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nSpec-Driven Development: Practical Guide Beyond Vibe Coding\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"f380cab5dd613857\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.linkedin.com/pulse/spec-driven-development-from-vibe-coding-structured-ai-alain-bouchard-xbjae/\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"8a9cf51c0f33ab0c\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nSpec Driven Development is the practice of writing a structured specification before writing code, especially when working with AI assistants. The specification defines requirements, architecture ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"8a9cf51c0f33ab0c\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.linkedin.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"dbfa6e51fb8e4c51\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nFrom Vibe Coding to Enterprise Engineering - Medium\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"dbfa6e51fb8e4c51\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://medium.com/@andrea.schiona/from-vibe-coding-to-enterprise-engineering-da4204b3286a\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"26c1e5c87b9f70cc\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nFrom Vibe Coding to Enterprise Engineering How to scale AI coding agents with Spec‑Driven Development , standards, guardrails, and repeatable patterns (with a full GitHub Spec Kit \\\"Hello …\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"26c1e5c87b9f70cc\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"medium.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"f8c2cfb7da59d72f\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nHow AI-DLC Implements Spec-Driven Development: From Technique to ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"f8c2cfb7da59d72f\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://buildwithdc.substack.com/p/aidlc-implements-spec-driven-development\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"affe5e8fcd797fac\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAt the time of writing, Spec- Driven Development is still continuously being evolved. The definitions in this article are accurate as of November 2025 . Spec- driven development transforms AI -assisted programming from ad-hoc \\\"vibe coding \\\" to structured development using specifications as \\\"super prompts.\\\" These version-controlled documents serve as North Star guidance for AI agents ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"affe5e8fcd797fac\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"buildwithdc.substack.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"f212766bcd968048\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nGoodbye Vibe Coding: Spec-Driven Development Framework for Structured ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"f212766bcd968048\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://pasqualepillitteri.it/en/news/158/framework-ai-spec-driven-development-guide-bmad-gsd-ralph-loop\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"999cab276805f45a\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nWhat is Spec- Driven Development ? A methodology where specifications become first-class executable artifacts. You write the \\\"spec\\\" (structured documentation) first, then the AI generates code that respects that contract. The spec becomes the source of truth for developers and AI agents, eliminating the ambiguities of vibe coding .\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"999cab276805f45a\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"pasqualepillitteri.it\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"54ed4419b9e9f37d\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nSpec-Driven Development: The 2026 Guide to Production AI Code\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"54ed4419b9e9f37d\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.productbuilder.net/learn/spec-driven-development\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"117874ed6227ae32\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nThe complete 2026 guide to spec- driven development . Learn how Claude Code Skills, GitHub Spec Kit, Amazon Kiro, and AI coding agents turn structured specifications into production-ready code.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"117874ed6227ae32\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.productbuilder.net\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"query":"specification driven development SDD AI coding enterprise practice 2025 2026 comparison","provider":"duckduckgo","count":10,"tookMs":2991,"externalContent":{"untrusted":true,"source":"web_search","provider":"duckduckgo","wrapped":true},"results":[{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"d458f20c93eb620d\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nSpec-Driven Development: From Code to Contract in the Age of AI Coding ...\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"d458f20c93eb620d\">>>","url":"https://arxiv.org/html/2602.00180v1","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"f2ae7fd82c407eae\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nSpec- driven development ( SDD ) [2, 4] offers an alternative: make the specification the source of truth, and let code derive from it. Instead of coding first and documenting later (or never), teams write clear specifications of intended behavior, then generate, implement, or verify code against those specifications .\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"f2ae7fd82c407eae\">>>","siteName":"arxiv.org"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"3a7194bcb3ad22a8\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nAgentic Coding: GSD vs Spec Kit vs OpenSpec vs Taskmaster AI: Where SDD ...\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"3a7194bcb3ad22a8\">>>","url":"https://pub.spillwave.com/agentic-coding-gsd-vs-spec-kit-vs-openspec-vs-taskmaster-ai-where-sdd-tools-diverge-0414dcb97e46","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"883b0c153fd10dd3\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nSpec- driven development has gone mainstream. The premise is straightforward: define what you want before writing code, then let AI agents generate the implementation from structured specifications . In early 2025 , this was a niche workflow. By early 2026 , four spec- driven development tools with a combined 137,000+ GitHub stars have turned it into a movement.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"883b0c153fd10dd3\">>>","siteName":"pub.spillwave.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"a237ff4b76fc3649\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nSpec-Driven Development (SDD): A Technical Deep Dive into the ...\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"a237ff4b76fc3649\">>>","url":"https://www.rushis.com/spec-driven-development-sdd-a-technical-deep-dive-into-the-methodologies-reshaping-ai-assisted-engineering/","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"e199d166f8cc9a92\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nVibe coding broke as fast as it shipped. Spec- Driven Development is the industry's course correction — putting structured specs, not chat prompts, at the center of AI -assisted engineering. This post compares the leading SDD frameworks, their trade-offs, and when (or whether) to adopt one.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"e199d166f8cc9a92\">>>","siteName":"www.rushis.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"92fbdaf374eef6f0\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nSpec-driven development: Unpacking one of 2025's key new AI-assisted ...\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"92fbdaf374eef6f0\">>>","url":"https://www.thoughtworks.com/en-us/insights/blog/agile-engineering-practices/spec-driven-development-unpacking-2025-new-engineering-practices","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"720b772c871efe3a\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nDefining spec- driven development and competing interpretations of it My understanding of spec- driven development ( SDD ) is that it's a development paradigm that uses well-crafted software requirement specifications as prompts, aided by AI coding agents, to generate executable code.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"720b772c871efe3a\">>>","siteName":"www.thoughtworks.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"47452defc128ade8\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nComplete Guide to Spec Coding (SDD): The Path to AI Engineering at ...\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"47452defc128ade8\">>>","url":"https://qubittool.com/blog/spec-coding-complete-guide","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"b0d9fbbb021f48ca\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nTL;DR: If Vibe Coding lets you \"run fast,\" Spec Coding (Spec- Driven Development , SDD ) ensures you \"run far.\" In 2026 , the engineering consensus is clear: in the AI era, code is no longer the asset— the specification is the asset. And OpenSpec is the most widely adopted open-source framework for putting this into practice . This article deconstructs this structured paradigm and teaches you how ...\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"b0d9fbbb021f48ca\">>>","siteName":"qubittool.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"f380cab5dd613857\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nSpec-Driven Development: Practical Guide Beyond Vibe Coding\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"f380cab5dd613857\">>>","url":"https://www.linkedin.com/pulse/spec-driven-development-from-vibe-coding-structured-ai-alain-bouchard-xbjae/","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"8a9cf51c0f33ab0c\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nSpec Driven Development is the practice of writing a structured specification before writing code, especially when working with AI assistants. The specification defines requirements, architecture ...\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"8a9cf51c0f33ab0c\">>>","siteName":"www.linkedin.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"dbfa6e51fb8e4c51\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nFrom Vibe Coding to Enterprise Engineering - Medium\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"dbfa6e51fb8e4c51\">>>","url":"https://medium.com/@andrea.schiona/from-vibe-coding-to-enterprise-engineering-da4204b3286a","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"26c1e5c87b9f70cc\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nFrom Vibe Coding to Enterprise Engineering How to scale AI coding agents with Spec‑Driven Development , standards, guardrails, and repeatable patterns (with a full GitHub Spec Kit \"Hello …\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"26c1e5c87b9f70cc\">>>","siteName":"medium.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"f8c2cfb7da59d72f\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nHow AI-DLC Implements Spec-Driven Development: From Technique to ...\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"f8c2cfb7da59d72f\">>>","url":"https://buildwithdc.substack.com/p/aidlc-implements-spec-driven-development","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"affe5e8fcd797fac\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nAt the time of writing, Spec- Driven Development is still continuously being evolved. The definitions in this article are accurate as of November 2025 . Spec- driven development transforms AI -assisted programming from ad-hoc \"vibe coding \" to structured development using specifications as \"super prompts.\" These version-controlled documents serve as North Star guidance for AI agents ...\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"affe5e8fcd797fac\">>>","siteName":"buildwithdc.substack.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"f212766bcd968048\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nGoodbye Vibe Coding: Spec-Driven Development Framework for Structured ...\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"f212766bcd968048\">>>","url":"https://pasqualepillitteri.it/en/news/158/framework-ai-spec-driven-development-guide-bmad-gsd-ralph-loop","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"999cab276805f45a\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nWhat is Spec- Driven Development ? A methodology where specifications become first-class executable artifacts. You write the \"spec\" (structured documentation) first, then the AI generates code that respects that contract. The spec becomes the source of truth for developers and AI agents, eliminating the ambiguities of vibe coding .\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"999cab276805f45a\">>>","siteName":"pasqualepillitteri.it"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"54ed4419b9e9f37d\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nSpec-Driven Development: The 2026 Guide to Production AI Code\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"54ed4419b9e9f37d\">>>","url":"https://www.productbuilder.net/learn/spec-driven-development","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"117874ed6227ae32\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nThe complete 2026 guide to spec- driven development . Learn how Claude Code Skills, GitHub Spec Kit, Amazon Kiro, and AI coding agents turn structured specifications into production-ready code.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"117874ed6227ae32\">>>","siteName":"www.productbuilder.net"}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775552703027}}
