{"type":"message","id":"a43ef4e1","parentId":"da49becd","timestamp":"2026-04-07T09:15:25.851Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_9def709518b245dfb1bf2a7c","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"| Tesla | Model-Based Development | 自动驾驶控制 | 安全关键系统验证 |\n\n---\n\n## 三、SDD 的本质\n\n[263 more lines in file. Use offset=180 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775553325849}}
