{"type":"message","id":"745ffc36","parentId":"73ac3d18","timestamp":"2026-04-07T10:57:45.695Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"你说得对，GSD 那行引用标记 [25] 在参考来源里确实没有对应条目。这是我的疏漏。\n\nGSD 是 \"Get Shit Done\" 的缩写，一个社区 SDD 工具，GitHub 仓库是 `gsd-build/get-shit-done`，来自 Spillwave 的对比文章。有两个处理方式：\n\n1. **去掉 GSD 列** — 文章主线是 Spec Kit / OpenSpec / Superpowers / Kiro 四个工具，GSD 不是必须的\n2. **补上引用** — 在参考来源中加上 GSD 的链接\n\n你觉得哪种好？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":120644,"output":135,"cacheRead":10287,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":131066,"cost":{"input":0.1447728,"output":0.00054,"cacheRead":0.0024688799999999997,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.14778168000000003}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775559429733,"responseId":"20260407185725a1ccb1e9f5814586"}}
