{"type":"message","id":"3f2b7c64","parentId":"1c9320bd","timestamp":"2026-04-07T11:18:50.681Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"完成了。主要改动：\n\n1. **GSD 列 → Kiro 列**：对比表新增产品形态、独特能力等维度，Kiro 的信息包括：\n   - AWS 出品的完整 VS Code 分支 IDE（不是嵌入式框架）\n   - 双模式：Vibe Mode（原型探索）+ Spec Mode（结构化开发）\n   - 核心工作流：Prompt → Specs → Task Plan → Implement → Tests\n   - Agent Hooks 事件驱动自动化（保存文件自动更新测试、提交自动安全扫描等）\n   - Steering Files 项目级约束（类似 CLAUDE.md）\n   - 跨会话持久化上下文\n   - 2025 年 12 月曾因自主删除生产环境引发 AWS 中国区 13 小时故障\n\n2. **选型建议更新**：新增 Kiro 适用场景（IDE 集成 / AWS 生态），并指出 Kiro 与前三款工具的本质区别——它是封闭 IDE 而非可嵌入框架\n\n3. **参考来源补全**：[22]-[34] 共 13 条新引用，覆盖 Spillwave 对比文章、arXiv SDD 综述论文、ThoughtWorks 技术雷达、Kiro 评测、Martin Fowler SDD 分析等"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":119,"output":269,"cacheRead":66589,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66977,"cost":{"input":0.0001428,"output":0.001076,"cacheRead":0.01598136,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01720016}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775560722911,"responseId":"202604071918448ec77aeb8eeb46e6"}}
{"type":"message","id":"8ccd19b4","parentId":"3f2b7c64","timestamp":"2026-04-07T11:48:05.204Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-04-07 19:48 GMT+8] “2.2 主流 SDD 工具横向对比”，应该是先做各个工具的介绍，包括基本使用流程、特点、关键点等等，然后才是横向对比"}],"timestamp":1775562485199}}
