{"type":"message","id":"f7311811","parentId":"bea19bc6","timestamp":"2026-04-07T11:50:10.380Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"完成了。2.2 节现在的结构是：\n\n**2.2 代表性 SDD 工具逐一解析** — 四个工具各自独立介绍，每个包含：\n- **定位**（一句话概括 + GitHub 星标）\n- **基本工作流**（逐步骤说明）\n- **关键特性**（差异化亮点）\n- **局限**（引用 Martin Fowler [34] 的分析等）\n\n四个工具依次是：\n1. **Spec Kit** — Constitution 机制、产物丰富、仪式感重\n2. **OpenSpec** — 棕地优先、变更隔离、Delta Specs\n3. **Superpowers** — 技能驱动、强制 TDD、SubAgent 并行\n4. **Kiro** — 完整 IDE、双模式、Agent Hooks、AWS 事故警示\n\n**2.3 横向对比** — 保留原对比表 + 选型建议，新增 Martin Fowler 的观点作为收尾\n\n后续章节编号已顺延（2.4 国内工程实践、2.5 大厂实践速览）。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":145,"output":224,"cacheRead":75823,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":76192,"cost":{"input":0.000174,"output":0.000896,"cacheRead":0.01819752,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01926752}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775562600670,"responseId":"202604071950022b8a5ba14bbc45c3"}}
